1] The Composition is a design technique to implement HAS-A relationship

2] Composition is achieved by instance (Class level) variable that refers to other objects

3] Composition Definition: If an object contains other objects, and the object cannot exist without the contained object, then that is called composition

4] Composition Def2: way of describing reference between Two or more classes using Instance variable

5] Multiple inheritance is not supported in Java, but it can be achieved using Composition